body_html: I think the issue is that, when sample_distorted_bounding_box switched to V2, min_object_covered has been changed form an attr to an input. As input could not have a default value like attr, min_object_covered=None will result in an error. Created a PR #15531 for the fix.

body: I think the issue is that, when sample_distorted_bounding_box switched to V2, min_object_covered has been changed form an attr to an input. As input could not have a default value like attr, min_object_covered=None will result in an error. Created a PR #15531 for the fix.
